Keep Favorite Report Folders in View

Pin your most-used report and dashboard folders to the top of the folder list so you donâ€™t have to scroll down every time you need them.

Available in: Salesforce Classic (not available in all orgs)
Available in: All Editions

In the list of report and dashboard folders, hover over any folder, then click .
Select Pin to top.
Your folder moves to the top of the folders list.

Each new folder that you pin goes to the top of the list, above any folders you have already pinned. To move a pinned folder back to the top, pin it again.
title: Keep Favorite Salesforce Reports Top
